               <head>Collection of medical works</head>
               
               
               
               <msContents class="lccn.loc.gov/sh85083148" rend="visible">
                  
                  
                  
                  <summary>Medical works.</summary>
                  
                  
                  
                  <textLang mainLang="he"/>
                  
                  
                  
                  <msItem rend="">
                     
                     
                     
                     <locus from="1r" to="128v"/>
                     
                     
                     
                     <author>
                        
                        
                        
                        <persName xml:lang="en" key="viaf.org/viaf/112670997">Ibn Māsawayh, Yūḥannā, -857 or 858</persName>
                        
                        
                        
                        <persName xml:lang="he" key="viaf.org/viaf/112670997">מאסויא, יחיא אבן</persName>
                        
                        
                        
                        <persName xml:lang="ara" key="viaf.org/viaf/112670997">ابن ماسويه، يوحنا</persName>
                     
                     
                     
                     </author>
                     
                     
                     
                     <title xml:lang="he-Latn-x-lc">Refu᾿ot</title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <title xml:lang="he">רפואות  </title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <note>
                        
                        
                        
                        <p>Two treatises based on Mesue the elder's works. The first treatise deals with 64 simple medicaments (imperfect at the beginning, folio 2r), and the second with compound medicaments (folio 52r). </p>
                        
                        
                        
                        <p>The headings of the chapters do not entirely tally with the list given at the beginning of the manuscript. </p>
                     
                     
                     
                     </note>
                     
                     
                     
                     <colophon xml:lang="he">נשלם יום חמישי שני ימים לחדש מרחשון שנת <date calendar="Hebrew">רנ"ב</date> ליצירה במדינת <name type="place">טירואיל</name>. <locus n="128v"/>
                     
                     
                     
                     </colophon>
                  
                  
                  
                  </msItem>
                  
                  
                  
                  <msItem rend="">
                     
                     
                     
                     <locus from="129r" to="159v"/>
                     
                     
                     
                     <author>
                        
                        
                        
                        <persName xml:lang="en" key="viaf.org/viaf/232520321">Praepositus, Nicolaus </persName>
                        
                        
                        
                        <persName xml:lang="he" key="viaf.org/viaf/232520321">ניקולאוס פריפזיטוס</persName>
                     
                     
                     
                     </author>
                     
                     
                     
                     <title xml:lang="he-Latn-x-lc">Antidotarium</title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <title xml:lang="he">אנטידוטריום</title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <note>
                        
                        
                        
                        <p>In the Hebrew translation of Ya῾aḳov Ḳatan, with the translator's preface. </p>
                        
                        
                        
                        <p>The work contains 104 entries, marked by a later hand in ordinary figures in the margin, ending on folio 148v. A number of additional paragraphs follow, the last being numbered 170. The medicaments are not arranged alphabetically in the present manuscript. </p>
                        
                        
                        
                        <p>The recipes, etc., were written by later hands on folios 156v-159v. There are also here and there marginal additions in the body of the manuscript. </p>
                     
                     
                     
                     </note>
                  
                  
                  
                  </msItem>
               
               
               
